com.da.antiphish.analyse

Class Computer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.da.antiphish.analyse.Computer

  • public class Computer
extends Object
    Computer represents the controller of an analysis. It gets the input URL from the REST request, handles the analysis and returns the result.
    Author:
    Marco Madritsch

    • Method Detail

      • analyse

        public double analyse(String stringUrl)
        Analyses the website of the given URL. The final score is the sum of all weighted scores of the TaskResult objects.
        Parameters:
        stringUrl - the URL of the website
        Returns:
        the final score of the analysis as double between 0.0 and 1.0 if success, -1.0 otherwise

      • getTrafficLight

        public TrafficLight getTrafficLight(double finalScore)
        Returns the traffic light based on the given final score and the defined ranges in configuration file config.json.
        Parameters:
        finalScore - the final score of the analysis
        Returns:
        the corresponding traffic light
